# React SPA Patterns

## Stack

- Vite, React 19, React Router 7
- Local dev: **port 9000** (`pnpm dev`, `strictPort: true`)
- TanStack Query for server state
- `@edunudg/ui` for components
- `@edunudg/tenant` for host resolution

## Structure

```
apps/web/src/
  bootstrap/     # TenantProvider, auth init
  features/      # domain modules (platform, brand, center)
  routes/        # portal route trees
  lib/           # supabase client singleton
```

## Rules

- Colocate `Component.test.tsx` with features
- Route guards use `useTenant()` + `useMembership()`
- No direct `fetch` to Supabase REST — use `@supabase/supabase-js` client
- Dark mode via `ThemeProvider` in `@edunudg/ui`
